text: before we get started if you see an
error message during this process it's
likely due to your permissions go to
aws.amazon.com / artifact / FAQ for more
information about the specific error and
then contact your administrator ok let's
get started
log in to the AWS management console and
search artifact click the agreements tab
on the left hand side for this video
we're going to sign up for an AWS
business associate addendum or baa but
the process for signing up for other
agreements is the same click the arrow
read the agreement language that calls
out the terms of the AWS baa
for example signing up for a baa is an
agreement between you and AWS and terms
of our baa are confidential and subject
to NDA once you've read the specifics
click download and review the AWS baa
this window with our NDA will appear
read the NDA check the box if you agree
then click accept
NDA and download the AWS baa click the
PDF to read the baa once you're done go
back to artifact check all the boxes to
take responsibility for the terms and
then click the blue box to accept the
AWS baa for your account and that's it
you've just accepted an online agreement
with AWS click the arrow to confirm that
your agreement is active
